==Latin==
===Suffix===
'''-itas,''' ''f'',  '''[[Wiktionary Appendix:Latin third declension|-itātis]]'''

# suffix appended usually to adjectives to form a noun indicating a state of being.

====Examples====
*masculinus - masculinitas
*activus - activitas
*civis - civitas
*fidelis - fidelitas

